data.description: Panoramic views of the Oaks North Golf Course and mountains from this lovely top-floor condo! Enjoy the views from the living room, kitchen, both bedrooms, and back patio. Approximately a half mile from the Bernardo winery, golf cart zoned. This home has dual pane sliding doors and windows, quartz countertops and stainless-steel sink in the kitchen, tiled back and front patios, ceiling fans, full-size stackable washer/dryer and a utility sink in the laundry closet. The living room area has a built-in alcove that's perfect for an office.
